OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775559585
OL,3,CDrinks giant joins Pepsi in pulling
OL,4,Cout of festival over Kanye West
OL,5,Cheadliner
OL,7,FThe company behind Johnnie Walker and
OL,8,FCaptain Morgan drinks brands has
OL,9,Fjoined Pepsi in withdrawing its
OL,10,Fsponsorship of Wireless festival after
OL,11,Fit announced Kanye West as the
OL,12,Fheadline act.
OL,14,FMain sponsor Pepsi announced earlier
OL,15,Fon Sunday it would withdraw support
OL,16,Ffor the festival, which is due to take
OL,17,Fplace in July at Finsbury Park, north
OL,18,FLondon.
OL,20,FNow, drinks giant Diageo announced it
OL,21,Ftoo would withdraw support.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
