PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775559585
OL,3,CDrinks giant joins Pepsi in pulling
OL,4,Cout of festival over Kanye West
OL,5,Cheadliner
OL,7,FA spokesperson told ITV News on Sunday
OL,8,Fevening: "We have informed the
OL,9,Forganisers of our concerns and as it
OL,10,Fstands, Diageo will not sponsor the
OL,11,F2026 Wireless festival."
OL,13,FIt comes after Prime Minister Keir
OL,14,FStarmer called the decision to book
OL,15,FWest, also known as Ye, "deeply
OL,16,Fconcerning."
OL,26,@pD@JOUsD@XO]wD@YOUxD@LO]
