PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775559585
OL,3,CDrinks giant joins Pepsi in pulling
OL,4,Cout of festival over Kanye West
OL,5,Cheadliner
OL,7,FAs first reported by The Sun on
OL,8,FSunday, the Prime Minister said: "It
OL,9,Fis deeply concerning that Kanye West
OL,10,Fhas been booked to perform at Wireless
OL,11,Fdespite his previous antisemitic
OL,12,Fremarks and celebration of Nazism.
OL,14,F"Antisemitism in any form is abhorrent
OL,15,Fand must be confronted clearly and
OL,16,Ffirmly wherever it appears. Everyone
OL,17,Fhas a responsibility to ensure Britain
OL,18,Fis a place where Jewish people feel
OL,19,Fsafe and secure."
OL,26,@pD@bOUvD@AOU{D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
