OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775559585
OL,3,CDrinks giant joins Pepsi in pulling
OL,4,Cout of festival over Kanye West
OL,5,Cheadliner
OL,7,FThe musician apologised in January for
OL,8,Fhis antisemitic remarks in a letter
OL,9,Fpublished as a full-page advert in the
OL,10,FWall Street Journal newspaper.
OL,12,FIn his letter, he apologised to Jewish
OL,13,Fand black people.
OL,15,FHe said his bipolar disorder led him
OL,16,Fto fall into "a four-month-long, manic
OL,17,Fepisode of psychotic, paranoid and
OL,18,Fimpulsive behaviour that destroyed my
OL,19,Flife".
OL,26,@xD@NOU{D@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
