PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775559585
OL,3,CDrinks giant joins Pepsi in pulling
OL,4,Cout of festival over Kanye West
OL,5,Cheadliner
OL,7,FPhil Rosenberg, president of the Board
OL,8,Fof Deputies of British Jews, said it
OL,9,Fwas "absolutely the wrong decision" to
OL,10,Fallow West to play.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FThe 48-year-old rapper's appearance at
OL,18,FWireless Festival comes as fears of
OL,19,Fantisemitism grow within the UK.
OL,26,@qD@EOUqD@cO]
